	<description>
		<p>Quick PDF Join is a fast and easy-to-use PDF merging application.</p>
		<p>Features:</p>
		<ul>
			<li>adding, removing, reordering and clearing of PDF files</li>
			<li>multi-selection, when adding and removing PDF files</li>
			<li>joining of differently structured PDF files</li>
			<li>automatic compression of the output PDF file</li>
		</ul>
	</description>

